  <div class="blurb-box col-sm-offset-1 sunk-quote">
    <p><span class="large-quotes">&ldquo;</span>Beyond Z introduced me into the real world and how things work outside of academics! My interviewing skills have definitely grown and developed through my time at BZ. The networking I have done has exceeded any other time of my life, I have met some incredible people and stayed in touch with many of them. My decision to enter the Education field has been reinforced through my time at BZ as well, and all the connections I have made have impacted the way in which I think of approaching certain matters!<span class="large-quotes">&rdquo;</span>
    </p>
    <footer>- Martha Mendoza</footer>
  </div>
  <div class="blurb-box col-sm-offset-2 sunk-quote">
    <p><span class="large-quotes">&ldquo;</span>
    Beyond Z had provided me with innumerable opportunities for personal and professional growth, but the Capstone project took our learning experiences beyond that of our own and empowered me to give back to my community. I really appreciated this opportunity, it was a great learning experience in regards to leadership for me as a project manager.
    <span class="large-quotes">&rdquo;</span>
    </p>
    <footer>- Kelly Hernandez</footer>
  </div>
</section>

<hr />

<h2> Partner Voices</h2>

